<item>
            <title>[HBASE-4220] Lots of DNS queries from client</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4220</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In running a YCSB workload, I managed to DDOS a DNS server since it seems to be flooding lots of DNS requests. Installing nscd on the client machines improved throughput by a factor of 6 and stopped killing the server. These are long-running clients, so it&apos;s not clear why we do so many lookups.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
